14
00:01:04,729 --> 00:01:08,170
At the upper bounds of 0.75, that&#39;s very good.

15
00:01:08,170 --> 00:01:10,930
At the lower bounds of 0.4, that&#39;s moderate.

16
00:01:10,930 --> 00:01:16,500
So, intelligence tests generally seem to measure the things that we think they measure.

17
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:20,200
If someone does get a high IQ score, what does that tell us?

18
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:24,350
