22
00:01:34,810 --> 00:01:37,509
That&#39;s all an IQ score tells us.

23
00:01:37,509 --> 00:01:41,619
Having a good IQ isn&#39;t necessarily the only recipe for success.

24
00:01:41,619 --> 00:01:43,579
It&#39;s only part of the picture.

25
00:01:43,579 --> 00:01:49,229
It tells us about someone’s cognitive ability, but a lot of other things contribute to success.

